name: QrDecoded
summary: Result of decoding a QR code payload.

properties.name: ErrorCorrectionLevel
properties.summary: Gets the decoded error correction level.

properties.name: Text
properties.summary: Gets the decoded payload interpreted as text (ISO-8859-1 by default; respects ECI per segment).

properties.name: StructuredAppend
properties.summary: Structured append metadata when the payload participates in a multi-symbol sequence.

properties.name: Fnc1Mode
properties.summary: Indicates whether the payload uses FNC1 (GS1) mode.

properties.name: Parsed
properties.summary: Gets the parsed payload when recognized (URL, WiFi, contact, etc.).
